description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HR/ L&amp;D Administrator&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;£19,188pa pro rata&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Part Time – 25.5 hours per week&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1-year fixed term contract&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you the administrator that we are searching for?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are the Human Resources and Learning &amp; Development team at Benenden Hospital and are currently looking for an experienced Administrator to join their team on a one-year, part-time contract.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Can you:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;provide an outstanding administration service to a busy, fast-paced department?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;demonstrate good attention to detail whilst working to tight deadlines?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;manage internal and external stakeholders’ expectations whilst ensuring HR and L&amp;D policies are procedures are adhered to?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;extract specified information from an IT database and manipulate the data to provide accurate reporting?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;confidently provide first-line support to our colleagues across the hospital as well external parties via telephone, email and in person?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you can, we want to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ideally you will have experience of a HR and/or L&amp;D environment, but this is not essential as our team will be happy to share their knowledge and experience to help you learn.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What can we offer you?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a part-time role of 25.5 hours per week and you will be required to work on a Monday and a Friday with the remaining 15.5 hours flexibly throughout the week. This role is based on-site and we offer a COVID secure working environment in our state-of-the-art hospital, located outside the rural village of Benenden.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer a range of great staff benefits including an enhanced annual leave entitlement, defined contribution pension scheme, free car parking, subsidised prices in our on-site restaurant and membership of Benenden Health, an alternative healthcare service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that strict pre-employment checks are required for this role including a satisfactory standard disclosure and two references.&lt;/p&gt;
